Bobpoblo’s Gun Game Map Pack 2


These 13 maps are my latest releases put together in one zipped package for your convenience.  Many of the maps use custom textures, each map’s detailed information can be found at its respective page.  Some of the maps in the pack are labeled “fy_” but can still be used perfectly fine for Gun Game play.  Also, almost all of the maps have buy zones for fy_ style play.

You can find map pack #1 here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/114772

(63MB Packaged - 190MB Unpacked)
